downscaleR 1.3-0
=================

* New function `filterGrid` to apply time filters (moving averages...) to a grid
* New bridging function `easyVeri2grid` to convert `easyVerification` matrices to climatological grids
* Bug fix in attribute inheritance after member aggregation
* `plotMeanGrid` still available but deprecated. It has been superseded by `plotClimatology` 
* Minor bug fix in `makeMultiField` to preserve the climatology attributes
* Other minor bug fixes and enhancements



